InpRKM¶

toolbox.InpRKM(inp)¶

InpRKM function uses the object structure generated from the JSON data and returns the same structure with additional fields related to reaction kinetic model(RKM) necessary for setting up the COMSOL model.

Parameters:

inp – input

Returns:

inp output
